{"tid":1550293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警狗強姦...希望唔係真","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T00:30:58.000Z","uid":313031,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"346b08babd6999568a5485dc9e253d44f9d3c97b","tid":1550293,"uid":313031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFP5SHh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFP5SHh.png&h=bba3e893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n突然好想講<br />\n去到呢個地步仲認為佢班狗仲有誠信可言?!<br />\n唔出聲佢地就一定唔會做野<br />\n電視劇都有教 死人先至能保密<br />\n唔企出黎被消失分分鐘仲容易<br />\n起碼光明正大出黎有各路媒體睇住<br />\n一冇消息大家知咩事<br />\n唉.. 我無經歷當時人的痛 但真係希望佢呢世所有噩運已盡 接下來嘅時間只有開心嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFb post樓主而家講d唔講d 我地唔知佢邊個<br />\n但班警察就可能已經知佢邊個..<br />\nGod Bless Please...."},{"pid":"fcaaaf7ee84f156e811d43c423dd561a45b1d28a","tid":1550293,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:26:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7940ed6cb2ae4299fc61a27cd7f3af6e9becdb6e","tid":1550293,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply